Window can be open, closed
Radiator can be on, off
TV can be on, off

When Window.open then Radiator.off
When Radiator.on then Window.closed

When 20:15 then TV.off
When 20:00 then TV.on

When 22:00 then TV.off
When TV.on then {
	if (time > 22:00) {
		println("Isn't it too late for TV?")
		trigger(TV.off)
	}
}